  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 300F.",
    "Combine almonds, cranberries, and green onions in a mixing bowl.",
    "Add minced garlic, salt, black pepper, olive oil, and red wine vinegar. Mix well until all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Transfer the mixture into an 8x8 inch baking dish. Bake for 25 minutes or until lightly golden brown.",
    "Remove from oven and let it cool slightly before serving."
